**Amnesiac** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous | Limited
__Basics__
The Amnesiac has forgotten their role. At the end of Day 1, the Amnesiac remembers their role.
__Details__
At the start of the game, the Amnesiac has no powers, but at the end of Day 1, the Amnesiac changes into another townsfolk role. 
The role the Amnesiac will change into is not known to the players.
If the Amnesiac changes into a role that has a power limited to only Day 0/Day 1 or Night 1, they can instead using it during Day 2 or Night 2.
If they change into a role that receives information or is part of a group at the start of the game, the Amnesiac will receive the information or join the group directly after changing role.
